    <item>
      <title>以色列只有“哈马斯完全投降”才能结束加沙战争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/israel-will-only-end-war-in-gaza-with-total-surrender-of-hamas</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名高级官员表示，尽管国际社会要求其停止攻势的压力越来越大，但以色列坚称，在巴勒斯坦激进组织投降并归还其三个多月前俘虏的所有人员之前，其针对哈马斯的行动不会结束。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/israel-will-only-end-war-in-gaza-with-total-surrender-of-hamas</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 07:48:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾计划在南海建立前哨基地</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/philippines-plans-to-develop-outposts-in-south-china-sea</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾军方负责人表示，在与北京在有争议水域的紧张局势持续存在的情况下，该国正在寻求发展其在南海的前哨基地，并获取更多的海岸防御资产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/philippines-plans-to-develop-outposts-in-south-china-sea</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 05:57:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>经过 100 天的战争，以色列并没有退缩</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/israel-hamas-will-war-spread-to-hezbollah-and-axis-of-resistance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着对抗真主党的兴趣增加，问题仍然是冲突是否会从加沙蔓延并演变成一场更广泛的大火。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/israel-hamas-will-war-spread-to-hezbollah-and-axis-of-resistance</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 05:00:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
